            <strong>Note:</strong> This game was built in a hackathon for <a href="http://jsfoo.in/">JSFoo 2013</a>, a JavaScript conference in Bangalore, India. Since a lot of people are enjoying it, we decided to keep it up for anyone to play.
        </div>
        <p>
        	<ul>
        		<li>Concept and level design from Ryan Bates' <a href="https://github.com/ryanb/ruby-warrior">Ruby Warrior</a></li>
